data.description: **Price Drop**Cute Bungalow just needs a touch of TLC, Updated kitchen with Stainless Steal Appliances. Nice hardwood throughout the upstairs. Newer Roof, Furnace and Water Heater. Rare find for the area but this house has a 3 Car Garage and lots of yard to spare. Come take a look and enjoy a great home at an amazing value.
